    "faq.privacy.question": "Wie schützt securememo.app meine Privatsphäre?",
    "faq.privacy.answer": "securememo.app uses browser-side AES-256 encryption, meaning your memo is encrypted before being sent to our servers. We do not see the plaintext content. Memos are deleted after successful read confirmation or expiration, and we do not require user accounts.",
    "faq.encryption.question": "Welche Verschlüsselung verwendet securememo.app?",
    "faq.encryption.answer": "Wir verwenden AES-256-GCM-Verschlüsselung mit PBKDF2-Schlüsselableitung (2.200.000+ Iterationen). Alle Verschlüsselung findet clientseitig in Ihrem Browser mit der Web Crypto API statt. Das Verschlüsselungspasswort wird separat generiert und niemals auf unseren Servern gespeichert.",
    "faq.duration.question": "Wie lange halten Notizen?",
    "faq.duration.answer": "Memos can be set to expire after 8 hours, 1 day, 2 days, 1 week, or 30 days maximum. After a successful read, the browser confirms deletion with the server. Expired memos are automatically cleaned up every hour.",
    "faq.recovery.question": "Kann ich eine gelöschte Notiz wiederherstellen?",
    "faq.recovery.answer": "No. Once a memo has been deleted after successful read confirmation or expiration cleanup, it cannot be recovered.",
    "faq.cost.question": "Ist securememo.app kostenlos zu nutzen?",
    "faq.cost.answer": "Ja, securememo.app ist vollständig kostenlos zu nutzen. Es gibt keine versteckten Gebühren, keine Premium-Features und kein Tracking oder Werbung.",
    "faq.technology.question": "Welche Technologie verwendet securememo.app?",
    "faq.technology.answer": "securememo.app is built on a Go service for HTTP handling, SQLite database for storage, Web Crypto API for browser-side encryption, and modern HTML/CSS/JavaScript. The source code is open source and available on GitHub.",
